      <guid>https://kubectl.docs.kubernetes.io/installation/kustomize/homebrew/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;For &lt;a href=&#34;https://brew.sh&#34;&gt;Homebrew&lt;/a&gt; users:&lt;/p&gt;
